room_title: Escape room "The Principal's Office" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: You're in the sitting area awaiting your turn to speak with the principal. You are looking at suspension, expulsion or even worse. In 45 minutes, the principal will arrive, and you have to find a way to escape your fate! Search for clues but watch out, you may uncover some of the secrets the principal is hiding!
